            <tr bgcolor="#c2beb4">
                <td align="center">Crisostomo Ibarra is the main character of Noli Me Tangere. He studied in Europe for 7 years.</td>
                <td align="center">Maria Clara is the childhood friend of Crisostomo Ibarra</td>
                <td align="center">Don Rafael Ibarra is the father of Crisostomo Ibarra.</td>
                <td align="center">Father of Maria Clara. He is described as Pandak, hindi kaputian, may bilugang mukha at may katabaan. He is also the richest person in Binundok</td>
                <td align="center">Padre Damaso is a snobbish, ruthless and judgemental person, arrogant and pedantic priest.</td>
